


A) Unit tests (suggestion: tests on the cache behavior; tests on "data validation", "converters" or “utils” in general, if applicable).

B) Service level tests, with dependency isolation using mocks (suggestion: test your services in isolation from external data provider). 

C) Integration tests on your API (suggestion: Spring Boot MockMvc and/or REST-Assured).

D) Functional testing (on the web interface). Be sure to adopt a Behavior-driven approach (features with scenarios).

E) Integration of analysis with Sonar Qube(or Codacy). Note: If the Git project is public, it can be analyzed in SonarCloud.